{"tid":126893,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男/女朋友睇你舊相","createTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:43.000Z","uid":39137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efe1e2f1eb80a93f742ffedf414473abbdadc5cb","tid":126893,"uid":39137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:43.000Z","msg":"其實都有del同ex既合照架啦<br />\n亦都冇仼何留戀 淨係愛現任<br />\n今日女朋友無啦啦興起周圍碌想睇我舊相<br />\n我又驚會有漏網之魚(事實上真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n驚佢睇到會誤會 亂諗野<br />\n所以情急之下stop左佢<br />\n同佢講可能會見到啲刪漏既相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢事後話冇野<br />\n亦都有叫佢一齊睇一齊del相<br />\n但我都係怕佢會亂諗野<br />\n或者到我亂諗野啦<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}